ARM: 7981/1: add support for AT_HWCAP2 ELF auxv entry

This enables AT_HWCAP2 for ARM. The generic support for this
new ELF auxv entry was added in commit 2171364d1a9 (powerpc:
Add HWCAP2 aux entry)

